properties.Project_Summary: The specific plan and subdivision would allow for development of307 single family dwellings, 111 acres ofundevelopcd open space, hiking trails, and 9 acres of parks on the 352.8-acrc project site formerly known as the Martin Ranch. Primary access to the project site is planned as an extension ofVerdemont Drive. A secondary access road is proposed to connect the western portion of the site to the J-215 frontage road.
